<li><a href="http://congress.fightforthefuture.org/">Contact Congress (FFTF)</a> - Used to send emails to members of the US Congress. This is Fight for the Future's hosted-version of the open sources Contact Congress. Ideal for organizations that send a lot of emails to congress, but who don't have tech staff who can install and maintain their own version of the open source software.</li>
